16:["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-10 bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-500 p-6 rounded","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"Reason for ISO 27001 Information Security Standard"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 mb-4","children":"There are four fundamental business benefits that an organization can accomplish with the implementation of ISO 27001 Information Security standard:"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-3 text-gray-700","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-purple-700","children":"Legal Requirements:"}]," By implementing ISO 27001 standard, it gives you an ideal strategy to agree to the legal requirements."]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-purple-700","children":"Competitive Advantage:"}]," If an organization gets ISO 27001 certification and their competitors do not, then most of the customers move towards you and believe that their information will be safe."]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-purple-700","children":"Less Cost:"}]," Investment in ISO 27001 will tremendously reduce the cost by preventing the security incidents from happening."]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-purple-700","children":"Better Organizations:"}]," By implementing ISMS 27001, it settles down situations where workers are unsure of what needs to be done, helps the organizations to run their primary processes in a better way."]}]]}]]}]
